Signals
ctr-C
ctr-\
ctr-D
ctr-C in a prompt after you wrote some stuff
ctr-\ in a prompt after you wrote some stuff
ctr-D in a prompt after you wrote some stuff
ctr-C after running a blocking command like cat or grep without arguments
ctr-\ after running a blocking command like cat or grep without arguments
ctr-D after running a blocking command like cat or grep without arguments

